COPY (SELECT EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP()) AS ctime, a.schemaname, a.relname, a.indexrelname, idx_scan, idx_tup_read, idx_tup_fetch, idx_blks_read, idx_blks_hit FROM pg_stat_all_indexes a, pg_statio_all_indexes b WHERE a.indexrelid = b.indexrelid) TO STDOUT (FORMAT CSV);

CREATE INDEX lineitem_l_partkey_l_quantity_l_shipmode_idx
ON lineitem (l_partkey, l_quantity, l_shipmode);
